drug_candidates = []
for compound in hits:
    props = tu.run({
        "name": "RDKit_calculate_drug_properties",
        "arguments": {"smiles": compound['smiles']}
    })
    if props['lipinski_pass']:
        drug_candidates.append(compound)
```

